Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.67,0:29:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we tried to demonstrate it up here.\NUh you see sometimes mysteriously
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.79,0:29:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,strange things happen recurrently in\Nyour life. There's no rational
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.00,0:29:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,explanation.\NThere was one series of rather very
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.27,0:29:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,strange kinds of events and they kept\Nrecurring all over in different
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.67,0:29:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,countries and different circumstances\Nand the same kind of a thing would
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.96,0:29:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,recur. I mean, I just knew there was\Nsomething. I didn't believe in karma in
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.15,0:29:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,those days, but I knew it was something\Non some other level. And I would tell my
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.20,0:29:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,analyst about it.\NAnd he say, "It's just your paranoia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.76,0:30:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're connecting this all together, you\Nknow, is a logical sequence because
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.84,0:30:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the quality of the human mind." I\Nsaid, "That's true." But just
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.00,0:30:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,statistically, it's very, very unlikely,\Nyou know, that these strange things
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.72,0:30:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,would occur. And of course later on when\NI did check it out karmically
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.32,0:30:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,uh then it just verified what I sort of\Nintuited as a fact. Then the question is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.88,0:30:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,now what do you do about it? Well, you\Npray very intensely
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.03,0:30:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and whatever the defect was in a past\Nlife that accounts for this, you refute
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.60,0:30:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it. Um, declare one's choice of the\Nopposite,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.48,0:30:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,dedicate one's life uh to the opposite.\NSo, if you've been miserable towards uh
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.96,0:30:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,little dogs, you know, let's say this\Nlifetime you're always getting bitten by
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.15,0:30:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,dogs, you know what I'm saying? You\Nbegin to wonder. I mean, is there
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.55,0:30:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,something about me? The dogs hate me or\Nwhat the hell is it? You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.39,0:30:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be in the middle of nowhere and\Ndog comes out of somebody's apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.44,0:31:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and bites you in the leg. You begin to\Nwonder if you were once cruel to dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.24,0:31:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and tortured them to death or something.\NAnd if you ask, you'll find out, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.08,0:31:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you did. You were sort of a satist in\Nthat lifetime and chopped them up and uh
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.44,0:31:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying? So any anyway,\Nit does make it u more comprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.32,0:31:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to, you know, when we're\Ntalking about causality and overcoming
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.20,0:31:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the illusion of causality,\Nthen I would just explain to you how I
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.67,0:31:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,saw the universe when that state came on\Nthat
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.84,0:31:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the most shocking thing initially was\Nnot only the translucence and the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.72,0:31:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,oneness of all things\Nand the intensity of the divinity had
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.32,0:31:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,shown forth through all of creation.\NBut the awareness that everything was
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.15,0:32:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,happening spontaneously as as a result\Nof
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.96,0:32:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,its expression of his essence. Each\Nthing is the perfect expression of its
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.20,0:32:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,own essence as it manifests at this\Nmoment of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.15,0:32:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is happening spontaneously of\Nits own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.15,0:32:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you see that, you're get\Ntransported to a different realm. In
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.39,0:32:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,this realm, the illusion is that\Neverything is creating something else
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.00,0:32:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,from elsewhere.\NEverything is therefore dependent on
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.84,0:32:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,something outside of itself.\NEverything is dependent on some external
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.55,0:32:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,explanation for its existence\Nwhich misses the essence of reality that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.12,0:32:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,each thing is being what it is\Nspontaneously because that's the way it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.39,0:32:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,expresses its essence\Nat this moment in the context of these
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.24,0:33:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions. Huh? Understand? Is that\Ncomprehensible?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.15,0:33:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing is being merely being what it\Nis.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.39,0:33:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the cat and there sits his\Ncat and I was just struck with the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.03,0:33:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,profound\Nperfection of his exquisite catnness.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.00,0:33:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sitting there\N101% radiating catnness and not anything
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.67,0:33:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,else. And it's not that catnness is not\Ncoming from elsewhere. is not dependent
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.96,0:33:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,on anything outside of itself, but it's\Nthe unfoldment of its potentiality to be
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.91,0:33:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a perfect kitty as it sit there sits\Nthere and purr it's perfection at that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.00,0:33:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,moment. It is being absolutely 100% the\Ninfinite potentiality of kittiness at
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.91,0:33:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that moment. Right?\NIt's not dependent on anything outside
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.15,0:33:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of itself to be what it is.\NIt's not dependent on anything outside
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.96,0:34:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of itself to be what it is. So each one\Nof us is at the same in the same way
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.00,0:34:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,free then to express the potentiality of\Nthat which we are as we are created in
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.27,0:34:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the context of our current karma and the\Nconditions of the world. No right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.63,0:34:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So\Nuh
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.04,0:34:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,uh this has to do with the way the world\Nis going and uh as I said I I saw that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.44,0:34:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the world went from 190\Nwe saw for one thing the world went from
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.07,0:34:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,190 to prevailing to 207.\NThat's extremely important because you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.72,0:34:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,see in a balance if it's one feather to\Nthis way or one feather to this way when
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.48,0:34:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you project out a laser beam of infinite\Nnumber of millions of miles you're quite
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.15,0:35:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,away quite away from here under here.\NYou understand what I'm saying? The
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.00,0:35:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,slightest variation\Nwhen projected throughout the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.83,0:35:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness of all of mankind over\Neons of time. So the destiny of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.96,0:35:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is profoundly different than what it\Nwas. At 190 nuclear wipeout was almost
