Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.59,0:37:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he was the wrong guy. I mean, I don't\Nknow. That'd be pretty hard to live
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.32,0:37:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with. Uh, so it gives you no chance to\Ncorrect an error. No chance to correct
