Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.80,0:38:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness of mankind is\Nadvancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.00,0:38:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed to me up to uh the\Nconsciousness level of 190
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.24,0:38:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that mankind could was called homo\Nsapien. Homo sapien
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.48,0:38:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and\Nthe evolution of the humankind. There
