Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.20,0:38:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The homo sapiion calibrated\Nat 190 up to the year 1986
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.35,0:39:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the consciousness level jumped\Nto 207. A very very critical
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.59,0:39:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because it changes quality just like\Nwater at 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.07,0:39:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it's ice and solid here it's\Nliquid. So consciousness is 190 changes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.07,0:39:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,quality when it goes over 200.\NNow, it seems to me this signals the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.04,0:39:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,birth of Homo Spiritus.\NHomo sapiion has gone as far as he can
