Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.04,0:39:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,military machines. And what did he do\Nwith it? Used it to destroy innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.28,0:39:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,people.\NNo, it seems to me that the birth of a
