Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.04,0:40:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever those people are the Afghani\Nbomber types? We uh we look out for
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.83,0:40:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,their human rights. We you know what I'm\Nsaying? That's homo homosspiritus
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.96,0:40:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to even question what is the right of\Nthe accused
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.80,0:40:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,mass killer who would never have come up\Nat the lower levels. You just execute
