Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.76,0:40:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the political extreme of absurdity, the\Nmere fact that it is given countenance
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.11,0:40:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in today's society means the birth of a\Nnew greater and more intense spiritual
