Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.56,0:41:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly 911 has certainly seen the\Nrebirth of moral consciousness in
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.59,0:41:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,America. It's the endless. In fact,\Nthat's the content of the endless debate
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.96,0:41:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is what is the moral way to respond to\Nthis? What is the moral responsible
