Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.56,0:41:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it here.\NI remember I was at that lecture in the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.80,0:41:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,year 2002 and\Nyou tell your grandchildren
