Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.31,0:42:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh golly. All right. So there are\Ndisruptions in one's personal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.76,0:42:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Becoming spiritually committed can lead\Nto very major disruptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.56,0:42:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can walk away from a very intense uh\Nworldly commitment and just turn your
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.20,0:42:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,back on it and drive off with an old\Ntruck full of bunch of old tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.40,0:42:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it all behind. All the oriental\Nrugs and the antiques and the and and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.64,0:42:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the and all that. Just walk away from\Neverything, which leads some of your
