Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.19,1:47:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and needs a friend. God needs a friend.\NGod needs a friend in all of us. Every
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.67,1:47:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,kind word is a good way of thanking God\Nfor our existence. We'll take one last
