Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.40,1:49:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,digs with a small shovel will get\Nfarther than a person with a small
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.88,1:49:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,commitment but\Nuh um a major capacity for intellectual
