Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.40,1:50:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody else, no matter where in time\Nor space, including all of history, and
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.04,1:50:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you're already there, so you don't need\Nanything complicated.
